				<td colspan="2"><span>Red Scale:
<br />

<br />
I admit, I got lucky on mine, was camping Eldrig when a farming druid came by and dropped Talendor.  I immediately asked how much he'd sell them for, and he came over and GAVE them to me after verifying why I wanted them.
<br />

<br />
If that hadn't happened, we got probably 15-20 of them from killing the ghost in The Hole in preparation for killing Guardian of the Seal.  About the same difficulty as VS in KC, was trivial with 3 groups of 65's, we killed him with about 24 average 58 or so the first time.  Get a couple higher levels, could probably single-group with ease.
<br />

<br />
White scale:  Months of bazaar camping, got it for 7k (average price was 60k over this time).
